<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10622568>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Female of Nesiophasma sobesonbaii n. sp. A. HT, dorsal view [IMQC, ex coll. FH]. B. HT, lateral view [IMQC, ex coll. FH]. C. Head and prothorax in dorsolateral view [FH]. D. Head and prothorax in dorsal view [FH]. E. Head and prothorax in ventral view [FH]. F. Right profemur in ventral view [FH]. G. Left mesofemur in posterolateral view [FH]. H. Left mesofemur in ventral view [FH]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10622568/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10622578>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Live Nesiophasma sobesonbaii n. sp. A. ♀ (brown form) at Kupang on guava (Psidium guajava (Myrtaceae). B. ♀ (brown form) with mating ♂ on its back (captive reared). C. Ventral view of metathorax of brown captive reared ♀ showing the orange coxae. D. Typical green ♀ (captive reared). E. Lateral view of head, pro- and mesothorax of green ♀ showing the red stripe of the mesopleurae (captive reared)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10622578/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10622572>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Terminalia and egg of Nesiophasma sobesonbaii n. sp. A. Terminalia of ♀ in lateral view [FH]. B. PTerminalia of ♀ in dorsal view [FH]. C. Terminalia of ♀ in ventral view [FH]. D. Terminalia of ♀ in lateral view, showing details of inner genitalia [FH]. E. Terminalia of ♂ in lateral view [FH]. F. P Terminalia of ♂ in dorsal view [FH]. G. Terminalia of ♂ in ventral view [FH]. H. Egg in dorsal view [FH, No. 1311-E]. I. Egg in lateral view [FH, No. 1311-E]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10622572/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10622570>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Male of Nesiophasma sobesonbaii n. sp. A. PT, dorsolateral view [FH, No. 1311-8]. B. PT, head and prothorax in dorsolateral view [FH]. C. Head and prothorax in dorsal view [FH].D. Head and prothorax in ventral view [FH]. E. Apical portion of right mesofemur in posterolateral view [FH]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10622570/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10622580>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Live Nesiophasma sobesonbaii n. sp. ♂ (captive reared). B. Closeup of head and prothorax of ♂ (captive reared). C. Green ♀, closeup of head and thorax (Captive reared). D. ♀ brown colour form (captive reared)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10622580/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10622576>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. A-B. Natural habitat of Nesiophasma sobesonbaii n. sp. at Desa Oemasi SE of Kupang (400 m), Nekamese District, Province East Nusa Tenggara." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10622576/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10622574>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Distribution and records of Nesiophasma sobesonbaii n. sp. (CopyrightWikimedia Creative Commons (GFDL, CC-BY, PD). Mats Halldin,CC BY-SA 3.0 (original file slightly adjusted):https://de.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Datei:East_Timor_map_mhn.jpg)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10622574/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

